<bibRefCitation author="Svihla, V." box="[610,756,187,215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="427" refId="ref6923" refString="Svihla, V. (2008) Order Coleoptera, family Oedemeridae. In: Harten, A. V. (Ed.), Arthropod fauna of the United Arab Emirates. Vol. 1. Multiply Marketing Consultancy Services, Abu Dhabi, pp. 264 - 269." type="book" year="2008">Švihla, 2008</bibRefCitation>
